{"tid":1507473,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我話畀大家知，咩叫各有各做","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:01:47.000Z","uid":222614,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"760b345e0c223afdccef42fab66d63e7f818d494","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"831，和理非去民陣既遊行，義士去中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n對義士既好處：減少前線偽勇武，唔洗下下造成不必要恐慌<br />\n對和理非既好處：唔洗擔心有義士偏離遊行目的，疑神疑鬼<br />\n<br />\n咁樣就係「兄弟爬山，各有各做」既最佳體現！"},{"pid":"8863ee76800de7c8c6101a1cfe91241089acbd73","tid":1507473,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=ffa1a66a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"1bd25e250a632114b36aed4f889a58f52390c389","tid":1507473,"uid":185990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n集思廣益  對付白色恐怖嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506382\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506382</a>"},{"pid":"2c6570e1684407752bf9cf000e4c5602942ec60c","tid":1507473,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"[突發]撐狗學生寫左封信比人民日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n借推"},{"pid":"79c4bab3d809292c44826a1379fca60e5ef04d08","tid":1507473,"uid":64935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"勇武無和理非係後面充人數好易比狗突擊"},{"pid":"d6f2ae6cd07b3be58cb59c35bbdcae8fccfacfb7","tid":1507473,"uid":71423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:23:53.000Z","msg":"831叫人入機場=直接增加前線被捕風險<br />\n唔好妄想你叫得郁全世界轉入機場 <br />\n觀塘個日就係最好例子 更何況民陣？<br />\n<br />\n叫人入機場唔該9月1"},{"pid":"eab5c8cdde599910ea29a93346e68936fffadea3","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"抗爭者當中，義士只佔大約 20%，即係十個人當中，只有兩個真勇武<br />\n唔去民陣既大遊行，對整體人數黎講無太大影響<br />\n<br />\n但如果地區行動裡面摻入大量和理非，就會對義士既行動造成不便<br />\ne.g. 和理非好興突然轉身走，令到義士好多時都不知所措<br />\n又有部份激進和理非會極力阻礙義士既行動<br />\n<br />\n所以最適合既做法，就係按現時和理非同義士既比例實行「各有各做」"},{"pid":"fb553db777250f276c17c2fd95fbe2d40ab98f4e","tid":1507473,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c095281e773cc0fb5c17bb99cf8f13ad8cc01094","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79c4bab3d809292c44826a1379fca60e5ef04d08","tid":1507473,"uid":64935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"勇武無和理非係後面充人數好易比狗突擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"地區行動入面，人數唔係重點<br />\n已有無數次，即使我方人數多過敵方幾倍，都會被衝散<br />\n<br />\n只要適當運用資源先係最終既解決方法<br />\n<br />\n人多有人多既做法，人少有人少既行動，最重要係上下一心，毫無雜質"},{"pid":"6387ba4486e9f4fef1443d715094167cfae541c0","tid":1507473,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1．13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogleDrive: 91機場文宣資源 (手足有新貨話我知，會Upload上去)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY4bCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=54f0505e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n----------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>英文文宣建議：</strong></span><br />\n內容:<br />\n91 Hong Kong International Airport<br />\nSOS: Humanitarian Crisis Alert<br />\nGovernment has failed us. Police shot us.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s now or never, please stand with HK.<br />\nThanks in advance for your support and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n方向/ 建議：<br />\n-強調事態之緊急及嚴重<br />\n-形式係事先通知，而非道歉，機場示威是出師有名同埋其中既正當性<br />\n-例如可用&rdquo;SOS&rdquo;之字眼<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04wmZVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04wmZVM.jpg&h=efdc3dd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wVcXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wVcXg.jpg&h=05fc61c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLLrqSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLLrqSL.jpg&h=724c5863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06a6744e64bfefb56d47ff9ab58097fa1202c2f4","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"地區行動入面，有以下幾個 case（前提係純義士參與）<br />\n<br />\n1. 目標未佈防，我方人少：迅速行動，迅速撤離<br />\n2. 目標未佈防，我方人多：行動直至哨兵發現敵方開始增援，然後部署撤離<br />\n3. 目標已佈防，我方人少：尋找新目標<br />\n4. 目標已佈防，我方人多：設路障，對峙，投擲，干擾，然後視乎形勢進攻或撤離"},{"pid":"15e8dbc07a345a9fc4348e2166ab5fa9c57222f6","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:45:54.000Z","msg":"畀負評既唔該嘗試反駁一下"},{"pid":"d641a5acfed259b48540b16dcd5f68d87fc54ef5","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"245cea81f61216716bca8fdf0d3f8d16dd7a25db","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:49:52.000Z","msg":"831, 兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"9854f1def6b83dcda5e613e6a0b0edef0f3443a2","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得有一位義士講過：<br />\n「我地既然選擇要去，就已經有死既準備，如果依家你驚既，就唔好跟埋黎」"},{"pid":"74f1946acf3aabaa25930a59033aba55b201b57a","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"831, 兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"295d069c7f4b54a929bb4029447e014ef6fe95a9","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"831, 兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"391d62db4a3593a2e2bcbc142f7e51441dee7098","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"831, 兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"e69be9215c4f2e7b0875e44041fa355b58e6e664","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"831, 兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"1eb11fff18081b0c61aaa7524e359f63b32af332","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"16e341345dda17973d3f1279bbc3d283c82db58d","tid":1507473,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:59:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9786